Create Contract Prices and Discounts Using a Flow

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Developer, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

Admins and users with the Manage Flow permission can create contracts from quotes.

The Create Contract From Quote flow helps sales reps give customers the contract prices and discounts that they establish in their business relationship for future use.

In Setup, enter flow, select Flows under Process Automation, then select the Create Contract From Quote screen flow. Customize the standard flow to suit your business.
